title: Robert D'Ambrosia, MD Endowed Fund for Diversity in Orthopedics
description: To provide flexible resources for the greatest diversity initiative needs including but not limited to: lectureships, leadership development and training, student support and other programs in the Dept. of Orthopedics at the CU Anschutz Medical Campus.
